<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>LLM on apowerfulmei</title><link>https://apowerfulmei.github.io/tags/llm/</link><description>Recent content in LLM on apowerfulmei</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Tue, 10 Jun 2025 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://apowerfulmei.github.io/tags/llm/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>调用本地大模型进行predict</title><link>https://apowerfulmei.github.io/p/hello-local-llm-predict/</link><pubDate>Tue, 10 Jun 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://apowerfulmei.github.io/p/hello-local-llm-predict/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="本地大模型调用">本地大模型调用
&lt;/h1>&lt;p>最近用Lora微调了一个小模型，生成一些小程序，记录一下我是怎么在本地部署使用的。&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="实验环境">实验环境
&lt;/h2>&lt;p>A800 80G GPU
Qwen3 1.7b&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="使用模型进行推理">使用模型进行推理
&lt;/h2>&lt;p>大模型部署好以后，怎么调用大模型进行推理工作呢？整个流程可以分为4步：&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>初始化&lt;/li>
&lt;li>构建输入&lt;/li>
&lt;li>大模型生成&lt;/li>
&lt;li>解析输出&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;h3 id="初始化">初始化
&lt;/h3>&lt;p>在这一步，我们将加载本地大模型和分词器，使用Hugging Face的&lt;code>from_pretrained&lt;/code>函数。&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">5
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">6
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-python" data-lang="python">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="n">model&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">AutoModelForCausalLM&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">from_pretrained&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;./Qwen&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="n">device_map&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;auto&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="n">trust_remote_code&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="kc">True&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="n">tokenizer&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">AutoTokenizer&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">from_pretrained&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;./Qwen&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h3 id="构建输入">构建输入
&lt;/h3>&lt;p>在这一步，我们构建prompt作为输入，首先构造一个基础的消息文本。&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">4
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-python" data-lang="python">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="n">messages&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">[&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;role&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;system&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;content&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="sa">f&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="si">{&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">prompt&lt;/span>&lt;span class="si">}&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">},&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;role&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;user&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;content&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="sa">f&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="si">{&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">prompt_u&lt;/span>&lt;span class="si">}&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">}&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">]&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>然后用分词器构造template，将文字文本转化为大模型可以处理的输入格式。&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">5
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">6
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">7
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">8
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-python" data-lang="python">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="n">text&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">tokenizer&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">apply_chat_template&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="n">messages&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="n">tokenize&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="kc">False&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="n">add_generation_prompt&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="kc">True&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="n">enable_thinking&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="kc">False&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="n">model_inputs&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">tokenizer&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">([&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">text&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">],&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">return_tensors&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;pt&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">to&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">device&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>看看model_inputs直接打印出来输出的内容。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://apowerfulmei.github.io/p/hello-local-llm-predict/input_ids.png"
width="1432"
height="484"
srcset="https://apowerfulmei.github.io/p/hello-local-llm-predict/input_ids_hu_5aca08fef658bdc9.png 480w, https://apowerfulmei.github.io/p/hello-local-llm-predict/input_ids_hu_6f748edef6e5bf25.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="input_id"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="295"
data-flex-basis="710px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>可以看到分词器将文字转化为了模型可理解的数字序列，每个数字对应分词器词汇表中的一个词/子词。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;code>tokenize=False&lt;/code>参数会让函数以文本的形式输出结果，否则将以id的形式输出结果。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;code>add_generation_prompt=True&lt;/code>会在输出的结果中增加一个assistant的操作，这里我们将text以文本的形式打印出来看看。
&lt;img src="https://apowerfulmei.github.io/p/hello-local-llm-predict/assistant.png"
width="514"
height="216"
srcset="https://apowerfulmei.github.io/p/hello-local-llm-predict/assistant_hu_2c42730e23df5259.png 480w, https://apowerfulmei.github.io/p/hello-local-llm-predict/assistant_hu_65930f6dbd88f2fb.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="assistant"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="237"
data-flex-basis="571px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;code>enable_thinking&lt;/code>则是决定是否要启动大模型的思考模式，启动以后会延长思考时间，这里我直接关闭了。&lt;/p>
&lt;h3 id="使用模型进行推理-1">使用模型进行推理
&lt;/h3>&lt;p>这一步，我们将上一步得到的输入传递给大模型进行推理，得到推理结果。&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">5
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-python" data-lang="python">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="n">generated_ids&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">model&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">generate&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="n">model_inputs&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">input_ids&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="n">max_new_tokens&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">MAX_LENGTH&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="n">temperature&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="mf">1.0&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>这里输出的generated_ids也是以id的形式展现的，要使用tokenizer将其转换为自认语言。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://apowerfulmei.github.io/p/hello-local-llm-predict/generate.png"
width="1034"
height="150"
srcset="https://apowerfulmei.github.io/p/hello-local-llm-predict/generate_hu_a248b6755d24b56.png 480w, https://apowerfulmei.github.io/p/hello-local-llm-predict/generate_hu_6d8023a1f354fd1f.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="generate_id"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="689"
data-flex-basis="1654px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;h3 id="解析输出">解析输出
&lt;/h3>&lt;p>这一步，我们将大模型的输出解码，转为自然语言。&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">5
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">generated_ids = [
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> output_ids[len(input_ids):] for input_ids, output_ids in zip(model_inputs.input_ids, generated_ids)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">]
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">response = tokenizer.batch_decode(generated_ids, skip_special_tokens=True)[0]
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="推理加速">推理加速
&lt;/h2>&lt;p>跑着跑着，我就发现一些不对劲了，怎么生成速率这么慢？我统计了大模型进行10次推理任务所需的时间，生成一个1500 token长度的程序得花上&lt;strong>37s&lt;/strong>，这对吗？&lt;/p>
&lt;p>这不对，要知道我用的是个小模型，结果速度还不如网页大模型。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>后面找到了一些加速的方法，请容我细细道来。&lt;/p>
&lt;h3 id="增大-batch-size">增大 batch size
&lt;/h3>&lt;p>简单来说就是在tokenizer中添加多个请求内容，让大模型同时处理，生成多个response。最大化GPU计算单元利用率​。这个过程很像&lt;strong>并发&lt;/strong>。&lt;/p>
&lt;h3 id="使用多个gpu">使用多个GPU
&lt;/h3>&lt;p>这自然就没什么好说的。&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="完整程序代码">完整程序代码
&lt;/h2>&lt;h3 id="初始版本">初始版本
&lt;/h3>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
